    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of an order containing five families of freshwater and marine ray-finned fish, including ricefish, medakas, needlefish, flyingfishes, halfbeaks, and sauries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
